fm: int minPathSum(vector<vector<int> > &grid) {     int rows = grid.size();      if (0 == rows) {       return 0;     }      int cols = grid[0].size();     int row;     int col;      for (row = 1; row < rows; ++row) {       grid[row][0] += grid[row - 1][0];     }      for (col = 1; col < cols; ++col) {       grid[0][col] += grid[0][col - 1];     }      for (row = 1; row < rows; ++row) {       for (col = 1; col < cols; ++col) {         grid[row][col] += min(grid[row - 1][col], grid[row][col - 1]);       }     }      return grid[rows - 1][cols - 1];   }
